room_title: Escape room "The Executive Order" by Enter The Enigma in Colorado Springs
room_address: 3540 N. Academy Blvd Colorado Springs, CO 80917
room_description: You've learned that The President is set to sign an Executive Order that could change the way the world views the United States. With the help of a White House aide, you and your fellow journalists have been given one hour to get into the Oval Office and find the Executive Order to break open this story before the Secret Service finds you.
